OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Alec
OL,4,CPenstone
OL,6,FAlec Penstone, Age 99, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 3 June 2023
OL,10,FA technician specialising in detecting
OL,11,Fsubmarines, Alec Penstone was on board
OL,12,Fthe escort aircraft carrier HMS
OL,13,FCampania on D-Day as it played a vital
OL,14,Frole in protecting the troops landing
OL,15,Fon the beaches.
OL,17,FHe had been on the Arctic convoys to
OL,18,FRussia before his crew was diverted.
