OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Alec
OL,4,CPenstone
OL,6,F"As night fell on 5 June everything
OL,7,Fhappened. I was on an escort ship, a
OL,8,Fconverted merchant ship. We had
OL,9,FSwordfish and Wildcats (aircraft) on
OL,10,Fboard and overnight all our planes had
OL,11,Fbeen painted with white stripes to
OL,12,Fshow they were friendly planes.
OL,14,F"And then in the early hours of 6 June
OL,15,Fall hell broke loose. I was 27 feet
OL,16,Fdown beneath the waterline and the
OL,17,Fonly communication I had with the
OL,18,Fbridge was a telephone.
