OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Alec
OL,4,CPenstone
OL,6,F"And we heard then that it was an
OL,7,Finvasion and we were going over to
OL,8,FNormandy.
OL,10,F"We were the cover force protecting
OL,11,Fthe invading craft from the U-Boats.
OL,12,FWe were kept quite busy. We were
OL,13,FAction Stations for nearly 40 hours.
OL,14,FWithout us there would have been a
OL,15,Fmassacre. We weren't the only ships
OL,16,Fdoing it.
