OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Alec
OL,4,CPenstone
OL,6,F"Everyone was doing their bit as well.
OL,7,FOne did get through from the North
OL,8,FAtlantic and managed to torpedo one of
OL,9,Fthe ships with all the troops on but
OL,10,Fthat was the far side."
OL,12,FMr Penstone's ship was also an escort
OL,13,Fwhile cables were being laid across
OL,14,Fthe English Channel.
OL,16,FTwo oil pipelines, one from Dungeness
OL,17,Fin Kent and one from the Isle of
OL,18,FWight, supplied the advancing Armies
OL,19,Fin France in the weeks after the
OL,20,Finvasion.
